  local title="$1"
  cat <<EOF
---
title: "Postmortem: ${title}"
description: "Incident postmortem for ${title}"
author: "$(get_author)"
created: $(today)
updated: $(today)
status: draft
tags: [incident, postmortem]
---

# Postmortem: ${title}

| Field        | Value            |
| ------------ | ---------------- |
| **Severity** | P1 / P2 / P3    |
| **Date**     | $(today)         |
| **Duration** | HH:MM — HH:MM   |
| **Impact**   | [users/services] |
