  local title="$1"
  cat <<EOF
---
title: "Maintenance: ${title}"
description: "Planned maintenance window for ${title}"
author: "$(get_author)"
created: $(today)
updated: $(today)
status: draft
tags: [maintenance, operations]
---

# Maintenance: ${title}

| Field           | Value                          |
| --------------- | ------------------------------ |
| **Schedule**    | YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM — HH:MM (UTC+7) |
| **Duration**    | [X hours]                      |
| **Impact**      | [services affected]            |
| **Downtime**    | None / Partial / Full          |
| **Owner**       | [team/person]                  |
| **Approved by** | [approver]                     |

## Pre-checks

- [ ] Backup completed and verified
- [ ] Rollback plan ready and tested
- [ ] Stakeholders notified (>= 24h advance)
- [ ] Monitoring dashboard open

## Procedure

| #   | Step          | Command       | Verify            |
| --- | ------------- | ------------- | ----------------- |
| 1   | [description] | \`[command]\`   | [expected output] |

## Rollback

| #   | Step            | Command     |
| --- | --------------- | ----------- |
| 1   | [rollback step] | \`[command]\` |

## Post-checks

- [ ] All services healthy
- [ ] No error spike (15 min observation)
- [ ] Performance within SLA
- [ ] Stakeholders notified: complete
EOF
}

