  local title="$1"
  cat <<EOF
---
title: "Release Notes — ${title}"
description: "Release notes for ${title}"
author: "$(get_author)"
created: $(today)
updated: $(today)
status: draft
tags: [release, changelog]
---

# Release Notes — ${title}

**Date:** $(today) | **Author:** $(get_author)

## Highlights

- [Major feature 1]
- [Bug fix 1]
- [Improvement 1]

## New Features

| Feature        | Description         |
| -------------- | ------------------- |
| [feature name] | [brief description] |

## Bug Fixes

| Issue             | Fix                |
| ----------------- | ------------------ |
| [bug description] | [how it was fixed] |

## Breaking Changes

> [If any — describe migration steps]

## Known Issues

| Issue   | Workaround   | ETA Fix |
| ------- | ------------ | ------- |
